{"tid":1721330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我想講呢場運動係鬥長命","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:25:50.000Z","uid":200288,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"05f603deb12c05a19d2ccb815ea36c522b382609","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"一場對抗極權嘅社運，唔係話我地守著間大學幾多日，就可以成功。<br />\n<br />\n過往嘅五個月，我地啲抗爭手法一變再變，<br />\n所以令政權無所適從，無法應對。<br />\n響中大打仗嘅一晚，在場嘅手足，<br />\n腎上腺素爆燈，睇直播嘅，難以入睡，<br />\n但響中大勝仗之後，警方開始收力，<br />\n任由我地去做自己想做嘅嘢，<br />\n於是我地開始守大學，手足響大學留守，<br />\n食得唔好，瞓得唔好，得閒就玩下魔法，<br />\n得閒就堵下路，的確，過往幾日可能好爽好開心，<br />\n但我們必須注意嘅係，我地開始冇左底線，<br />\n手足非常暴躁，見到唔順眼嘅人就屌，郁下喊打，<br />\n畫面唔好睇，但我相信大家冇割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n唔分化唔割蓆的確唔係得個講字，<br />\n但希望手足們注意，一場運動嘅持久，<br />\n唔係睇你守到間大學幾耐，更重要嘅係，<br />\n手足要食得好，瞓得好，住得好，<br />\n身心都要好，先有命捱落去，<br />\n請停止不必要嘅動作，不必要嘅留守，<br />\n加大力度文宣，BeWater快閃，所有活動對準政權。我哋唔係要贏一日，要眼光放遠，贏個政權。<br />\n<br />\n唔好消磨己方長他人志氣，手足日日捱狗飯，但差佬食好瞓好，咁樣唔係辦法。<br />\n<br />\n黎明前嘅黑暗係最撚黑暗，唔好俾警方收力下嘅自由摧毁我地嘅形象，自由唔係用嚟放肆，自由係用嚟彰顯示威者嘅克制，大家堅持，保重身體。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明終將來臨，香港人必勝。 加油</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">利申：以上係發夢打機內容，純屬講故分享，請不要做非法行為</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb9c46fb8245b90f03ff8b16d87886b7819af9e6","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足加油"},{"pid":"b00514055bda16864d38d6ac0ef98bd3aa5469a8","tid":1721330,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb811fac6469199ed1ea2246306559f3a9f24251","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"不分化，不割蓆，不指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c71d3a88d905dd9571c30ccd8f096021de931","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"認同嘅幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa09430610f2b5df96de61c81c723317a8b3afc6","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"食好瞓好先有力打機架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf017ece0d206c143c9104271c6c83544331e97","tid":1721330,"uid":72962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"我認同"},{"pid":"2bcb9f889e461093b8970f386f67dd9d065b8b12","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"身心都好緊要"},{"pid":"d2815d03739b3446f05ffdbb5509babd4e4ae20d","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"自推10連 （1/10）"},{"pid":"2f4ae44b0d7c0eab0fd5a90617ffdeec8f62ea7e","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:11.000Z","msg":"自推十連（2/10）"},{"pid":"1ddfb140bb072e97eb85b7f532be33746cdce4a5","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"自推十連（3/10）"},{"pid":"da2fac2b5192233258406b2dea9af771ab509d17","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"自推十連（4/10）"},{"pid":"6937c1bdb86833a3a197662ac29c141e64cf8e04","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi