c=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8608c85686a3b2d90e6b14cd6ea95f1d38c2f3","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手推，想大家停一停諗一諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202efb92fd33ea93186d18b07d901d49d41ed356","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />霸飯堂煮飯有少少off topic呀 <br />\n我唔要瘋狂追求好warm嘅畫面，我要贏呀<br />\n大家要脫離同溫層"},{"pid":"3bde084ec0a40238d27062bb73911c18bfa1c768","tid":1721330,"uid":288118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"講得好。社會運動是連續的，今次成功使社會全面政治覺醒，但是，還有一班老人家，他們一日未離開，社會仍然有支持者。我們要鬥毅力，鬥長命，用十年時間，好好用各種方式，去影響主流，特別班比人洗腦的婦人、中產。衝前之餘，一定要顧後，未來是屬於我們的！"},{"pid":"0973522b093d275704dcfd9ba50df7e88167d95e","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bde084ec0a40238d27062bb73911c18bfa1c768","tid":1721330,"uid":288118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"講得好。社會運動是連續的，今次成功使社會全面政治覺醒，但是，還有一班老人家，他們一日未離開，社會仍然有支持者。我們要鬥毅力，鬥長命，用十年時間，好好用各種方式，去影響主流，特別班比人洗腦的婦人、中產。衝前之餘，一定要顧後，未來是屬於我們的！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"做文宣做統戰係好撚辛苦，但脫離同溫層令更多嘅人企響我地呢邊先係最重要嘅事，圍爐好正但贏唔到架，我哋要謹言慎行先可以fight底呢個政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a4759cb9c553c5ddb25af67a045fc9b0ec04fa","tid":1721330,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人入嚟討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f8b179de44c0491ce20ebaf9bfc6e07c9eeb28","tid":1721330,"uid":310107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14